  "body": "Error while building `0.4.8` code.\r\n\r\n```\r\nCompiling 1 file with 0.4.8\r\nError: write EPIPE\r\n    at WriteWrap.onWriteComplete [as oncomplete] (node:internal/stream_base_commons:94:16)\r\n```\r\n\r\nReproduce bug:\r\n- Go to the CryptoPunksMarket contract and copy it [link](https://etherscan.io/address/0xb47e3cd837ddf8e4c57f05d70ab865de6e193bbb#code). \r\n- Paste it in a .sol file in your hardhat project.\r\n- Add in your `hardhat.config.ts` this solidity compiler:\r\n```\r\n {\r\n                version: '0.4.8',\r\n                settings: {\r\n                    optimizer: {\r\n                        enabled: true,\r\n                        runs: 200\r\n                    }\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n```\r\n- `yarn hardhat compile`\r\n\r\ndependencies:\r\n```\r\n        \"@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers\": \"^2.0.2\",\r\n        \"@nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle\": \"^2.0.1\",\r\n        \"@openzeppelin/contracts\": \"^4.3.2\",\r\n        \"@typechain/ethers-v5\": \"^8.0.0\",\r\n        \"@typechain/hardhat\": \"^3.0.0\",\r\n        \"@types/chai\": \"^4.2.22\",\r\n        \"@types/mocha\": \"^9.0.0\",\r\n        \"@types/node\": \"^16.11.6\",\r\n        \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^5.2.0\",\r\n        \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^5.2.0\",\r\n        \"chai\": \"^4.3.4\",\r\n        \"eslint\": \"^8.1.0\",\r\n        \"ethereum-waffle\": \"^3.4.0\",\r\n        \"ethers\": \"^5.5.1\",\r\n        \"hardhat\": \"^2.6.7\",\r\n        \"prettier\": \"^2.4.1\",\r\n        \"prettier-package-json\": \"^2.6.0\",\r\n        \"prettier-plugin-solidity\": \"^1.0.0-beta.18\",\r\n        \"ts-node\": \"^10.4.0\",\r\n        \"typechain\": \"^6.0.0\",\r\n        \"typescript\": \"^4.4.4\"\r\n```",
